Sync All
Expunge Both

IMAPStore personal-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
User burke@libbey.me
PassCmd "sudo -u burke /usr/bin/security -v find-internet-password -g -a burke@libbey.me -s imap.gmail.com /Users/burke/Library/Keychains/login.keychain 2>&1 | grep '^password: ' | sed 's/.*\"\\(.*\\)\"/\\1/'"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMech LOGIN
CertificateFile /Users/burke/.mutt/Equifax_Secure_CA.cert

MaildirStore personal-local
Path ~/.mail2/personal
Inbox ~/.mail2/personal/INBOX

Channel personal-inbox
Master ":personal-remote:INBOX"
Slave ":personal-local:INBOX"
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-github
Master ":personal-remote:github"
Slave ":personal-local:github"
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-archive
Master ":personal-remote:[Gmail]/All Mail"
Slave ":personal-local:archive"
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-drafts
Master ":personal-remote:[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave ":personal-local:drafts"
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-sent
Master ":personal-remote:[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave ":personal-local:sent"
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-flagged
Master ":personal-remote:[Gmail]/Starred"
Slave ":personal-local:flagged"
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-trash
Master ":personal-remote:[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave ":personal-local:trash"
Create Both
SyncState *

Group personal
Channel personal-trash
Channel personal-inbox
Channel personal-github
Channel personal-drafts
Channel personal-sent
Channel personal-flagged
Channel personal-archive


